page.title: 07CLUBS IN RADCLIFFE
page.content:
{CAT CLUB: }YOU DO WORK,PLAY GAMES AND TALK ABOUT JESUS.IT'S VERY GOOD AT CAT CLUB AND THERE ARE LOTS OF GAMES. IT IS OPEN EVERY FRIDAY. {INTERS: }AT INTERS YOU PLAY GAMES AND TALK.IT IS OPEN FROM 7.30 TO 9.30 EVERY FRIDAY IN MILTOWN STREET. {ATHLETICS: }AT ATHLETICS CLUB YOU RUN,JUMP,POLEVAULT AND OTHER THINGS. {CUBS: }AT CUBS YOU WORK AND PLAY GAMES AND GO ON TRIPS. {BROWNIES: }AT BROWNIES YOU WORK, EARN BADGES AND PLAY GAMES. {CRICKET: }AT CRICKET CLUB YOU PLAY GAMES OF CRICKET AND PRACTICE CRICKET. {TENNIS: }AT TENNIS CLUB YOU PLAY TENNIS AND PRACTICE.IT IS OPEN FROM 6.30.
by STEVEN RYDING
